story.storyDescription: Sarah finds a dead body in the woods and uncovers a dark and deadly mystery.
story.title: Littlefield - Part 14

messages.text: Helena? Are you there? We’re almost at the front of the building
I can’t fucking believe you guys
Excuse me??
Since you tweeted that, do you know how many people came here??
They started shooting people...
so you need to turn around or you’re going to be hurt
We’re NOT fucking turning around. Where are my parents??
They’re in compound C
Well, you go to compound C and tell them we’re here.
And get your Dad to open the gate
Don’t you get it? My Dad CAN’T open the gate.
He’s not the one in charge here
But he CAN talk to someone and let them know the circumstances with our parents
You owe us here.
They aren’t going to let you in here
Our PARENTS are in there and they are going to let us in
I’m walking over to Compound C now. My Dad is over there, and I’ll ask him
Are you there yet??
No
WALK FASTER
Why are you being such a bitch to me??
I’m sorry, you don’t find anything wrong with the fact that...
you’re going along with staying behind those closed doors while so many people suffer?
Like you’re all fucking survival of the fittest...
when you’re the survival of the most fucking privileged.
I can’t help that my Dad is a cop and they feel they need him.
All of this is supposed to be over soon anyway
No it’s not. This is just the fucking beginning.
ARE YOU THERE YET
Yes.
Did you tell my parents we’re outside
Yes
They said you aren’t allowed to come in. Your parents would have to leave
...so they’d send them off where it’s dangerous and they could die...
rather than let in their family...
Well, you’d be doing that and it’s more than just you, is it not?
Fuck you. Let me talk to my sister.
By the way, we’re walking up to the gate right now. And most of us are armed.
I bet it’s crazy out there.
Which it wouldn’t have been at all if you left it alone
We wouldn’t have gotten past the guards otherwise
And by the way, you guys aren’t as armed as the people in here.
Don’t be stupid, or nobody will get out alive
Why is it that the fucking people supposed to be protecting us...
are worse than the dangerous flesh-eating people out here
I want to talk to my Dad
Now?
YES NOW! GIVE HIM YOUR PHONE SINCE THEY STOLE HIS
Honey, it’s Dad. Are you okay?? Can I call??
My phone is running low, so I can’t right now.
Sarah is with me though. She’s safe. Jared got her
Helena told us.
What is it like in there??
What do you mean??
Is it nice?
It’s set up like a neighborhood. So houses etc.
And they have room for you??
They were pairing us up with a family...
which is what first tipped us off that they weren’t going to let you in
Dad, it’s Sarah...
What happened to you?? We have been worried sick!
It’s a long story, and I’m sorry...
I went out when I shouldn’t have, but I’m safe.
And listen...Corinne and I want you two to be safe too.
And if that means you guys need to stay there, you have to stay in there
No
Listen to us. We have my friend Wayne here...
whose family has a safe place for us to stay too that nobody knows about.
When this blows over we can come back and find you
Sarah, this isn’t blowing over. Is there room for us on this farm?
They said yes.
We’re coming out to you. We didn’t think we’d ever see you again...
you are not going to deny us that right now
Dad please.
It’s only a matter of time, that everyone on the outside burns this place down.
Your mother is getting our stuff
Are they going to let you come out of the front gate??
No, you’re going to have to meet us at a back entrance.
The guard said that it’s about a half mile off the property North.
We go out a tunnel and meet you there
We’re heading back to the van to get there. It’s a green van.
Wayne’s Dad is armed so don’t worry
Okay
Dad...are you sure
We’re staying together as a family. That’s what family is for.
I love you Dad...
Dad, it’s Corinne. We’re in the van, driving around now.
It’s Helena again.
Oh...well...I don’t really know what to say to you.
I have a question
And what’s that
Is there room for one more in the van
What!? What about your Dad
My Dad left you for dead and I don’t want to be here.
You’re right. These people are horrible, or blind, or ignorant...
if they want to stay here while everyone else suffers. So is there room?
Jared said you can sit on his lap.
I’m grabbing my bag, I’ll meet you at the back entrance with your folks.
Are you serious??
Yes.
twenty minutes later
Helena and Corrine and Sarah’s parents shoved themselves tightly in the van.
They all headed West.
After shooting some of the flesh-eaters on the way, they were all able to safely get to the farm.
Their phones eventually died, and there was no power to charge them back up.
But they were all together with the hope that one day things would get better.
Though in the meantime, they knew they wouldn’t be living...just trying to survive.
